{"id":232138672,"title":"#心得 快樂檸檬  檸檬味十足的爆榨檸檬綠茶","content":"http://i.imgur.com/YF5s5rt.jpg\n今天去逛新店家樂福時發現\n原本的日出茶太換成了快樂檸檬\n黃色的裝潢給人一種愉悅的感覺\n\n賣的品項不多，特色的是現榨檸檬系列的飲料\n熱銷第一名是爆榨檸檬茉香綠茶，當然是毫不猶豫馬上點一杯來試試\n除了飲料之外還有賣雞蛋仔，算是雞蛋糕的翻版吧\n\n店家提供的是紙吸管\n拿到飲料拍完照馬上喝\n可以感受到濃濃的檸檬味，幾乎要蓋過綠茶的味道了\n突然有點後悔點了微糖，因為檸檬汁的味道有點酸\n建議有本錢的人可以點五分糖以上喝喝看\n\n偷偷問，有人知道快樂檸檬是哪邊來的飲料店嗎?\n看答案→ http://www.happy-lemon.com/tw/brand/brand-story.php\n\n喜歡我的文章，可以來粉絲團支持一下!\nHonest foodie 美食老實說\n更多分享：https://www.facebook.com/honestfoodietw/\n\n#快樂檸檬 #手搖飲料 #爆榨檸檬茉香綠茶 #honestfoodie #美食老實說","excerpt":"今天去逛新店家樂福時發現，原本的日出茶太換成了快樂檸檬，黃色的裝潢給人一種愉悅的感覺，賣的品項不多，特色的是現榨檸檬系列的飲料，熱銷第一名是爆榨檸檬茉香綠茶，當然是毫不猶豫馬上點一杯來試試，除了飲料之","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"fc52ee20-8732-41df-9751-49a8427187d6","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-09-21T11:52:38.294Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-21T11:53:20.171Z","commentCount":8,"likeCount":11,"tags":[],"topics":["手搖飲","手搖板","飲料"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"手搖","forumAlias":"boba","school":"國立臺灣大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":11}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/YF5s5rt.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"0998d642-f484-42ba-b32a-0abcfd614640","url":"https://i.imgur.com/YF5s5rtl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/YF5s5rtl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/YF5s5rtl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-21T11:52:38.294Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-21T11:53:20.171Z"},{"id":"0998d642-f484-42ba-b32a-0abcfd614640","url":"http://i.imgur.com/YF5s5rt.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/YF5s5rt","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/YF5s5rtl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-21T11:52:38.294Z","updat